{"tid":901670,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽今年50 佢成日都唔夜晚訓覺","createTime":"2018-11-14T07:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T08:16:10.000Z","uid":84789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11b3dcb90a55589549b6238e575721c65c1f3191","tid":901670,"uid":84789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"其實已經持續左好耐 大概8年到<br />\n不過幾年前都冇咁誇張 依家就愈來愈嚴重<br />\n有時我訓嘅時候 佢未訓<br />\n我醒左 佢都係未訓<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅作息係：<br />\n5、6點  訓覺<br />\n7點  叫我起身<br />\n8點 訓翻<br />\n2-4點 出街（不定時 不過都係呢個時段裡面）<br />\n5-7點 翻屋企<br />\n8點 食飯<br />\n10-4 點 打機 睇劇<br />\n<br />\n佢幾乎每日都係咁<br />\n有時候佢仲要中午出街 但係訓得幾個鐘<br />\n雖然佢可能5點訓 但係3點先起身買餸<br />\n都係一直咁樣係咪冇事架？<br />\n佢有講過可能係更年期 個人多野諗 多野煩 所以訓唔到<br />\n成日都攞住手機睇劇 或者同啲同鄉打牌（手機game）<br />\n我有啲擔心佢咁樣嘅作息會對身體唔好<br />\n定係佢生理時鐘已經固定左？"},{"pid":"e6cbc746c3a616d416b4f376b549e9c9384b852b","tid":901670,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"關你叉事？"},{"pid":"cdc467b59555e933ed63ebc4d05b29cfa95bb911","tid":901670,"uid":84789,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6cbc746c3a616d416b4f376b549e9c9384b852b","tid":901670,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"關你叉事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"咁又關你鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06620f2f8e0505249b06ae6f546782dd558f1209","tid":901670,"uid":118910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"其實定時的話無乜所謂最緊要自己舒服"},{"pid":"f07a6929d3606e9bd6f9803d494360047b9c75a2","tid":901670,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:06:14.000Z","msg":"關唔關更年期事?"},{"pid":"d394514b553f87b8dea7750f6ade86f6dc350013","tid":901670,"uid":197813,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e6cbc746c3a616d416b4f376b549e9c9384b852b","tid":901670,"u